result.text: This is called Famille rose zun vessel with phoenix-shaped handles and #deer herd design and this zun vessel has a round belly. There is a pair of red and green phoenix-shaped ears traced in gold between its shoulder and its belly. The main part of the decorative painting on the zun vessel takes green mountains and forests as the background. There are many sika deer in different postures in the painting. Some are running. Some are playing. And some are grazing. The whole picture looks full of life. In Chinese, "deer" (“鹿 lù”) is homophonic with “happiness” (“禄 lù” ). According to statistics, there are about 100 deer in the painting. So, this is indeed a “100-deer zun”. #CulturalRelics
